.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Libraries</h2><h3>Docking</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.rosettacommons.org/docs/latest/Home\">Rosetta</a> - A comprehensive software suite for modeling macromolecular structures. Used larely for protein-protein docking.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-07-14T01:58:45.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Libraries</h2><h3>Molecular Descriptors</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/bp-kelley/descriptastorus\">DescriptaStorus</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/bp-kelley/descriptastorus\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">81</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":81,\"repo\":\"bp-kelley/descriptastorus\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Descriptor computation(chemistry) and (optional) storage for machine learning.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-07-14T01:54:52.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Libraries</h2><h3>General Purpose</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/mojaie/MolecularGraph.jl\">MolecularGraph.jl</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/mojaie/MolecularGraph.jl\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-