, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2.9k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":2919,\"repo\":\"deepchem/deepchem\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Deep learning library for Chemistry based on Tensorflow</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-08T14:00:23.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Libraries</h2><h3>Machine Learning</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://pytorch-geometric.readthedocs.io/en/latest/\">pytorch-geometric</a> - A PyTorch library provides implementation of many graph convolution algorithms.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-08T14:00:23.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Applications</h2><h3>Visualization</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.openmolecules.org/datawarrior/index.html\">DataWarrior</a> - A program for data Visualization and analysis which combines dynamic graphical views and interactive row filtering with chemical intelligence.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-05T10:59:30.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Courses</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://bigchem.eu/alllectures\">BigChem</a> - All lectures of <a href=\"http://bigchem.eu/\">BigChem</a> (A Horizon 2020 MSC ITN EID project, which provides innovative education in large chemical data analysis.)</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-16T17:54:00.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Libraries</h2><h3>Visulization</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/3dmol/3Dmol.js\">3Dmol.js</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/3dmol/3Dmol.js\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;backgroun